And why? Gameplay doesn't matter what-so-ever, unless it's related to the visuals of their ability animations/icons.

I can't for the life of me play her even to an average level, but man do I love Irelia's design. Despite her face in her splash art being a tad generic, everything else is basically A+. You get the flowing blades as well as her adornment having more flow to its design.

